        <title>在Ubuntu 16.04上安装Cacti 1.1.10的完整指南</title>
        <link>http://localhost:1313/p/%E5%9C%A8ubuntu-16.04%E4%B8%8A%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85cacti-1.1.10%E7%9A%84%E5%AE%8C%E6%95%B4%E6%8C%87%E5%8D%97/</link>
